&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bank Band 5 Staff Nurse&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking dynamic individuals with strong interpersonal skills and have an enthusiasm for caring for our patients. We are passionate about constantly improving our service and delivering high quality care to our patients and strive to build upon our already excellent services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a bank nurse you will have a flexible schedule and this will provide an opportunity to develop clinical skills and knowledge base in all specialties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that you will need to attend the next available Assessment Centre on 25th November.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions please do not hesitate to contact k.araya@nhs.net or contact the Temporary Staffing Requitment team rsch.jointhebank@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
